      "widgets_values": [
        "GPT Image 2 Tile Upscale - Regenerative 3x2 (6 tiles)\n\nPipeline: Tile Crop -> preview tiles -> Extract (x6) -> Scale By Placeholder (x6) -> Tile Collect -> preview upscaled -> Tile Stitch -> preview + Save + print size.\n\nReplace each Tile Scale By / Placeholder with your GPT-Image-2 or NB2 upscaler node.\ntile_metadata flows linearly: TileCropAM -> TileCollectAM (passthrough) -> TileStitchAM.\nGrid preset 'method default' auto-selects the recommended grid for the chosen method."
